Package: fasterize
Title: Fast sf-to-raster conversion
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Noam", "Ross", , "ross@ecohealthalliance.org", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("EcoHealth Alliance", role="cph"))
Description: fasterize provides a drop-in replacement for raster::rasterize
   that (a) takes sf-type objects, and (b) is much, much faster.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
LazyData: true
URL: https://github.com/ecohealthalliance/fasterize
